102    public static Map<Integer, Class<? extends HistoryLog>> LOG_MESSAGE_IDS = new HashMap<>();
103    public static Map<Class<? extends HistoryLog>, Integer> LOG_MESSAGE_CLASS_TO_ID = new HashMap<>();
104
105    static {
106        for (Class<? extends HistoryLog> clazz : LOG_MESSAGE_TYPES) {
107            try {
108                LOG_MESSAGE_IDS.put(clazz.newInstance().typeId(), clazz);
109                LOG_MESSAGE_CLASS_TO_ID.put(clazz, clazz.newInstance().typeId());
110            } catch (IllegalAccessException|InstantiationException e) {
111                L.e(TAG, String.format("could not instantiate %s", clazz), e);
112                e.printStackTrace();
113            }
114        }
115    }
116
117    public static HistoryLog parse(byte[] rawStream) {
118        int typeId = Bytes.readShort(rawStream, 0) & 4095;
119//        if (typeId % 256 != typeId) {
120//            L.w(TAG, "typeId "+typeId+" is being corrected to "+(typeId % 256));
121//            typeId = typeId % 256;
122//        }
123        HistoryLog ret = parseWithTypeId(rawStream, typeId);
124        if (ret instanceof UnknownHistoryLog) {
125            L.w(TAG, "retry HistoryLog parse on typeId " + typeId + " => " + ((byte) typeId));
126            HistoryLog two = parseWithTypeId(rawStream, (byte) typeId);
127            if (two instanceof UnknownHistoryLog) {
128                return ret;
129            }
130            return two;
131        }
132        return ret;
133    }
134
135    private static HistoryLog parseWithTypeId(byte[] rawStream, int typeId) {
136        HistoryLog historyLog = null;
137        if (!LOG_MESSAGE_IDS.containsKey(typeId)) {
138            L.t(TAG, "unknown HistoryLog typeId "+typeId+": "+ Hex.encodeHexString(rawStream));
139            historyLog = new UnknownHistoryLog();
140            historyLog.parse(rawStream);
141            L.i(TAG, String.format("PARSED-EMBEDDED-HISTORY-LOG(typeId=%-3d, UNKNOWN): %s", typeId, Hex.encodeHexString(rawStream)));
142            return historyLog;
143        }
144
145        try {
146            historyLog = LOG_MESSAGE_IDS.get(typeId).newInstance();
147        } catch (IllegalAccessException|InstantiationException e) {
148            L.e(TAG, "could not instantiate "+typeId, e);
149            e.printStackTrace();
150            return null;
151        }
152
153        String name = MessageHelpers.lastTwoParts(historyLog.getClass().getName());
154        L.t(TAG, "found matching "+name+" HistoryLog typeId "+typeId+": "+ Hex.encodeHexString(rawStream));
155        historyLog.parse(rawStream);
156        L.i(TAG, String.format("PARSED-EMBEDDED-HISTORY-LOG(typeId=%-3d, %s): %s", typeId, name, historyLog.toString()));
157        return historyLog;
158    }
